{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act31side_level_act31side_03_beg","storyGroup":"act31side","storySort":6,"storyDependence":"act31side_level_act31side_02_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HS-3","storyName":"早芒种","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"年和夕因突然回到大荒城的兄长而感到不安。禾生和小满在田间遇到了一个自称久未归乡的商人。商人大方地表示，可以卖给二人一个“愿望”。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act31side/level_act31side_03_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act31side_03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":4,"next":6,"characters":["年","夕","禾生","左乐","小满","土木天师","愤怒的职农","愤怒的土木天师","愤愤不平的职农","禾下午睡的男性","衣着华丽的男性"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_monastery_nomal.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"姐姐。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"我跟着那位先生远走，才发现原来外面的天地和这大荒城大不相同。我们留在这里短短几十年，人类又琢磨出不少新奇玩意。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"炎国大地上还有各式各样的城市，除了望不到头的农田，还有华丽的宫殿，热闹的集市，样样有趣。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"我回来歇歇就走。这一趟还是出远门，不知道多少年才能回来。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"说起来，这大荒城也不是早些年艰苦的时候，能照料这片田地的人多得是，你真的不打算和我一起出去看看？","id":13},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"......姐姐，我发现，原来外面的大地与这大荒城也没有什么不同。","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"是啊。又走了几十年，还是百来年？想法总是会变的。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"见得多了，发现原来不论走到哪里，人到底只是人，这人间好像没什么意思......人心叵测，但其实也不难猜。","id":18},{"type":"text","text":"嗯。先生死前说的话，我吃透了。","id":19},{"type":"text","text":"姐姐......你还打算留在这里多久？","id":20},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"charslot","id":25},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/40/Avg_bg_bg_cottage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":27},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":28,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","duration":"0.7","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":33},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"喂——","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"怎么好不容易把你从那座山头揪出来，还是这么自闭？既然现在黍也不在，和我出去转转咯？","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"这里没什么新奇玩意，但是果蔬粮食的味道还真是移动城市的种植地块比不了的。对了，你是不是还从来没见过粮食是怎么酿成酒的？","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"心烦。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"天师府是不是又来找你麻烦了？","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/31/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":43},{"type":"multiline","name":"夕","text":"我怕天师府什么！","id":44},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":45},{"type":"multiline","name":"夕","text":"我就是......我......","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......有这功夫，你应该为外面一动不动的大家伙想想办法。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2c/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"天师们都去救灾了，我一个人能有什么办法，又不能亲自上手......","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"好无聊啊！还是让我看看，你今天画的是......","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":53},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"不行！","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"别这么小气嘛，没灵感的话我还能给你出出主意？","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"给我，出去——","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_imp_ancientsword_h","volume":"0.8","id":61},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"charslot","id":64},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","id":68},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"这么紧张？看来是真的有秘密。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"不是秘密，是烦心事。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"......天师府里的老家伙们是挺烦的，但其实奈何不了你什么。而且都有朝廷替我们打包票了，他们最多唠叨你几句。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"所以你在烦......“他”。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"我能感觉到他已经到了，从不藏掖的。我们怎么说也是一家人，不去看看？","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"我才不去。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"这么生疏啊......我听说他每次路过你的山头，都会带些搜罗来的当世最好的画作送你的，你可别嘴硬说你不喜欢。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......不一样了。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"你上次见他，是什么时候？","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"唔，还真记不清了。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"他手中的生意做得太大，被司岁台提醒了好几次，之后好像收敛了一点。最近几年就只是游山玩水，把炎国每座城市都挨个转了个遍。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"可司岁台盯他比盯我们要严密得多了。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"你怎么知道得这么清楚......","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"和司岁台打交道的时候，偷偷瞄了两眼他们的记事本——藏得没那么深的那部分。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"“生意做得太大”。我怎么记得，他不过只是个喜欢养蚕种桑，跟在黍身边的小呆子。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2c/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"最近一次见他的时候——就是你所谓的“路过”那时——我从画里探过一两眼。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2c/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"那眼神，浑，讨厌，和那个——","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"——和臭棋篓子一样，我懂的。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"而且臭棋篓子越狱那年，他人就在百灶。你以为这几年大炎对你我不闻不问，都主要盯着谁呢？","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"你觉得他俩勾搭上了？","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"不晓得。我还以为臭棋篓子只和令姐大哥关系好。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"但要是司岁台做下了这种判断，他也不可能像现在这样到处串门了。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"你又不是不知道他有多会做“人”，年年定期给司岁台上交的账本，每一笔生意、每一文的收支都记得明明白白，挑不出半点毛病。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"不论哪里的城市遇上天灾受了损失，他自掏腰包赈灾的速度比谁都快。就是看在这一点上，司岁台再怎么说也得留几分情面。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"你觉得他有几分好心？","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"到底也是我们的兄弟......我还能背后说他坏话？","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"这种事你少干了？","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"何况人间本就不存在我们这样的关系。“兄弟姐妹”......我倒是......","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":126},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"35,0","duration":"0.4","focus":"l","isblock":"true","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"你倒是？","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":129},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"滚。别凑过来。也别趁机偷看！","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_branchrupture","volume":"0.4","id":133},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_pendrop","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.3","id":134},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","action":"jump","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-35,0","power":"5","times":"0","duration":"0.5","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":137},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"好好好，别动手，别急。唉。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/80/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"“兄弟姐妹”。毕竟世俗意义上的骨肉亲情对我们来说并不成立......","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"可能几百年后，炎国的史官会专门发明一个词来形容我们这样的关系......或许吧。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"但你这嘴硬的别扭性子要是能改改，我们还能多搞几次家庭聚会来着。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"我什么时候嘴硬过？","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c3/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"所以说，你什么时候才愿意让我看看，你书房里的那十二幅画？","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":149},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......滚！","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"嗯，没错，是十二幅。哪怕是三姐消失后，你也一直留着她那一幅。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"——画上的那些人究竟是谁，想明白了吗？还是不愿意再想了？","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"总不能......连你的自画像......至今都还是无从下笔吧？","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/31/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年","text":"非要这么拧巴？","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/31/Avg_avgnew_2014_nian_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avgnew_2015_dusk_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夕","text":"......","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fc/Avg_avgnew_2015_dusk_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":160},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":161},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"charslot","id":164},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":166},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":167,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":169},{"type":"text","text":"一场暴雨。","id":170},{"type":"text","text":"天上的灰云已经散了，空气中还能闻到湿润的气味。","id":171},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2","duration":"0.7","id":173},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","duration":"0.7","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":175},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":177},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2","focus":"l","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":179},{"type":"dialog","id":180},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":182},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_button","volume":"0.6","id":183},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":184},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_airshiptakeoff","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"mach","id":185},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","channel":"mach","fadetime":"1","id":186},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":187},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"mach","fadetime":"5","id":188},{"type":"playsound","key":"$factory_low_drone","channel":"dro","loop":"true","volume":"0","id":189},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","channel":"dro","id":190},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":191},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_reedmarshes","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"crop","id":192},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","channel":"crop","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":194},{"type":"text","text":"左乐看到禾生咬了咬牙，按下了手中天师仪的开关。","id":195},{"type":"text","text":"紧接着，一种他没有见过的大型载具碾过田地，一排排的庄稼跟着倒了下去。","id":196},{"type":"text","text":"风刮过断了根而枯黄的阔大的叶，发出止不住的响声。像是傲慢的嗤笑——","id":197},{"type":"text","text":"灾害说来就来，说走就走。","id":198},{"type":"text","text":"人能奈这片天如何？","id":199},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2","focus":"l","id":201},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"这些作物就是要放弃了？","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"嗯。","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"这片地是我的第一块试验田，原本种的都是玉米。它们全都被含源石的污水浸过了，只能处理掉。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"一块地一旦被源石污染过，恢复起来异常困难。所以这片大地很辽阔，但是能用来耕作的土地却少之又少。","id":207},{"type":"dialog","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"玉米连芯子都是甜的，我小时候刚来大荒城第一次尝，觉得它是最好吃的东西。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我想让它好好地长在土里，让所有人都能尝到它的甜味，像我第一次吃时那样开心。","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#7$2","focus":"l","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":214},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"charslot","id":216},{"type":"text","text":"发动机声隆隆作响，只留下一片光秃秃的土地。","id":217},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":218},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","duration":"0.5","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"小禾——终于找到你了！","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"快走快走，工程他们轧了一片田，职农大叔和天师们吵起来了，你快去看看吧！","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"dro","fadetime":"2","id":228},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"crop","fadetime":"2","id":229},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"charslot","id":232},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":233},{"type":"playsound","key":"$factory_low_drone","channel":"act","loop":"true","volume":"0","id":234},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","channel":"act","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":236},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":237},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"act","fadetime":"2.5","id":239},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_carjolt","volume":"0.8","delay":"1","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"各位，灾害刚过，物资短缺，时间紧任务重，我们的工程耽误不起了。","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"这些田已经是决定要废弃了，各位就让条道，让我们把这些工具搬过去吧！","id":244},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"“废”？俩嘴唇一碰就开始胡说！这里种田的天师前两天才告诉过我，庄稼研究到了最关键的时候。","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"你们开着载具直接从我们田上碾过去，谁给你们的权力？","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"“丁卯号地块泥土样本检测到过量源石颗粒浓度”，这个意思就是说这片田已经被污染了，已经废——","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"这样的灾年年都有，怎么你们这些外面的人来了，这土地在你们嘴里就成了废地了？","id":251},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"你们这田地又没法挪，几场灾下来已经被污染了，不救田也是上面的决定......","id":253},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"今年已经是荒年，不救田可是要闹荒的！","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"你们是不是没见过早些年大批大批饿死人的时候？！轻飘飘一句话，说先工程就先工程，不仅不帮着救土地还轧了过去！","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"大荒城可是我们的地方！","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"......你说的这都是什么道理？","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"什么道理？","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"老天爷的道理！你大爷的......","id":262},{"type":"dialog","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":264},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shovel","volume":"0.2","loop":"true","channel":"chan1","id":265},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"chan1","fadetime":"1","id":266},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sandftsingle","volume":"1","delay":"0.7","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":268},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":269},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":270},{"type":"dialog","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"......","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"你打我？","id":273},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的土木天师","text":"......你大爷的！","id":275},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punchsp5","volume":"0.8","id":278},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","delay":"0.2","id":279},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"你大爷的！！","id":282},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"叔叔阿姨们，你们别打架呀......","id":284},{"type":"dialog","id":285},{"type":"charslot","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":287},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":288},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#6$1","duration":"0.5","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":290},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"王伯！","id":292},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"——这田......","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"你看看！这地刚被源石毁过一次，还没来得及救，他们这些人开着载具又来轧一次！","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤怒的职农","text":"一说话就搬出什么侍郎什么报告，谁认你那个侍郎？那人我见都没见过！","id":297},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"各位天师，我们似乎并没有收到任何有关废弃这片田地的通知？","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我记得之前应该已经决定了，优先抢救土地......","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"你还没有听说？工程物资的补给已经到位了。大荒城的改建昨天晚上就恢复动工了。","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"根据最新的土地受损检查结果，也重新评估了修复土地需要的成本。","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"得出的结论是，要放弃大荒城外围农田地块的改建，优先保障核心城的建设......而且，要做好随时移动核心城的准备。","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"为什么？！","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"之前土地的污染源研究清楚了吗？为什么急着下这样的判断？","id":307},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"天师府......更上层得出的结论。你要是不信，也可以去找资深天师确认。","id":309},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"n","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"禾生回过头看了看，几位职农怔怔望着被履带碾过的田垄，神色黯然。","id":313},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"几位前辈，如果最终天师府得出了要放弃田地的结论，我们都会听从安排的。","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"只是这些田，不仅是这里的大家干活的地方，也是人们的家。","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"既然还没有正式通知大家搬离。至少现在，恳请你们先把这些工程器械挪到别的地方去，好吗？","id":317},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"......好，我答应你。不过也就这几天的时间了。","id":319},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"多谢了。","id":321},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1246_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"我知道，你们年年守在这里耕种是辛苦，但是情况不一样了。","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"过去没有移动城市的时候，人们确实离不开这片地，可是现在的庄稼都搬上移动地块发展无土栽培了......","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"说实话，大荒城这片地也没有什么特殊的。","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"土木天师","text":"你们说要在这里研究有源石耐受性的庄稼，可是这么多年过去了，不也没什么结果吗？","id":326},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":328},{"type":"dialog","id":329},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1","id":332},{"type":"charslot","id":333},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":334},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":335},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":337},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":339},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我只是不确定......如果最终只能得到这个结果，“万顷”这项研究，根本没有推广应用的可能。","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......这么多年了，别说成果，一点希望的苗头都看不到。","id":342},{"type":"dialog","id":343},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"charslot","id":346},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","amount":"0","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":349},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":350},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":352},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1249_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤愤不平的职农","text":"小禾，你和那些人说什么了，他们就走了？","id":354},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"也没什么......","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"王伯......最近，大家还是抓紧收拾田地吧......","id":358},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"charslot","id":363},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":365},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_normal_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":366,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"大水牛？大水牛！你到底在发什么呆呀？","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我们现在要怎么办？听那些天师的意思，大荒城真的要搬走？这些田都要抛下？","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"乡长奶奶不知道在哪里，我们要不要去找她？","id":375},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":377},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......你说话呀！","id":379},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"如果大荒城有这样的变动，她应该是第一个知道的。她没有站出来，说明她也没有办法......","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我更没有办法......","id":382},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"你又说什么丧气话呢？","id":384},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"你说，当年的神农，会不会真的是个神仙啊......","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"不然的话，她是怎么能在那么艰苦的环境里，开辟出这么一片土地的......","id":387},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"神农是很厉害，可是现在的人们能把这片土地照顾好也很厉害。","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"要是随随便便就说放弃了，神农才要狠狠骂你呢！","id":390},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1","id":391},{"type":"dialog","id":392},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":393},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_kneelsnow_s","volume":"0.8","id":394},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":395},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":396},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"啊！","id":398},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"charslot","id":400},{"type":"text","text":"小满感觉脚下踩到了什么东西，慌慌张张收回了脚。稻谷晃了晃，一个人影直起身子。","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾下午睡的男性","text":"唉，扰人清梦啊......","id":402},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":404},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":405},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#2$1","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"0.5","id":406},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":407},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":408},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"正梦到稻谷丰收，突然一场天灾，生生把这场好梦给砸醒了。","id":410},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"哎呀！你这人怎么在田里睡觉啊，不怕别人踩到你吗？","id":412},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"你不是已经狠狠地踩到了我吗？","id":414},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"那还不是因为你躺得不是地方？","id":416},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"抱歉！这位先生，您没有伤到哪里吧？","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"伤倒是没伤，可是这好好的衣服上踩了这么大一个泥脚印，实在是......","id":420},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"明明是你......睡觉不看地方的大叔叔！","id":422},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"......走路不看路的小丫头。","id":424},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"小满......","id":426},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"那你说怎么办嘛！我帮你洗干净，还是赔你一件？","id":428},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"算了吧，我身上的物件都是走南闯北搜罗来的最精贵的东西，交给你洗，最后只会收到一团乱麻。","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"先生......您就是为大荒城带来救灾物资的人？","id":432},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"你倒是机灵。","id":434},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"我是个商人，早些年做生意攒下了一些本钱，听闻大荒城遇上了灾害就赶了回来，故乡有难，自然是要尽己所能帮一帮的。","id":436},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"你也是大荒城的人？你为什么会在田地里睡觉？你在这里没有家吗？","id":438},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"太久没有回来，这里风景都变了模样，没想到就迷了路......正好想问问，你们知道看影子戏的地方怎么走吗？","id":440},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"“影子戏”？那是什么？","id":442},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":443},{"type":"multiline","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"用秸秆编出花样，用布蒙着灯，照出花样的影子演戏","id":444},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":445},{"type":"multiline","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"——你们现在已经不看影子戏了吗？","id":446},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我没看到过......","id":448},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"那，你们如今庆祝丰收的地方在哪呢？","id":450},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"您是说大戏台吗？","id":452},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"那我知道，你顺着这条路走，看到第三棵大树，再左转就是啦，其实就在神农祠的后面。","id":454},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"嗯......神农祠倒是还在。不错。","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"多谢，你是第一个愿意给我指路的人，也算和你有缘。卖你一个愿望，什么都行。","id":457},{"type":"dialog","id":458},{"type":"charslot","id":459},{"type":"text","text":"男人伸出手，掌心躺着一枚圆润的石子，盈盈地摇晃着光芒。","id":460},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"这是什么？","id":462},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"一个愿望，什么都行。","id":464},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"愿望？","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我不信，你是商人，又不是神仙，难道我和你说了，它就真能实现？","id":467},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"我的确只是一名商人，不过生意做得大一点，什么都能买，什么都能卖。","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"但能和我做生意的机会不是人人都有的。","id":470},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......真的？","id":472},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"n","id":473},{"type":"text","text":"小满回头看了一眼站在身后的小禾，仔细想了想，又看回面前的男人。","id":474},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"（小声）我希望......","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"（小声）我希望大荒城年年丰收，岁岁平安。","id":477},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"好，这个愿望我卖给你了，那对应的，你要拿什么来买呢？","id":479},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"小满......这个人看上去很奇怪，我们还是走吧。","id":481},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我没有什么值钱的东西，你可别想骗我的钱。","id":483},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"也不用多么贵重，只要是你喜欢的、看重的物件，都可以拿来交换。","id":485},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"小禾！我可以吹那首曲子吗？","id":487},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":488},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"曲子？......哪首曲子？","id":489},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":490},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......","id":491},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"n","id":492},{"type":"text","text":"小满一噘嘴。","id":493},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......你真是个笨水牛！","id":495},{"type":"dialog","id":496},{"type":"charslot","id":497},{"type":"text","text":"远处，几只羽兽停在牧兽的背上，用它们长长的喙捉走牧兽身上的小虫。","id":498},{"type":"text","text":"牧兽闷着头吃草，羽兽蹦蹦跳跳，偶尔伸直脖颈，发出几声愉悦婉转的鸣声。","id":499},{"type":"text","text":"小满横起自己的笛子，放到嘴边。","id":500},{"type":"text","text":"风轻轻地伴奏。","id":501},{"type":"dialog","id":502},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":503},{"type":"gridbg","imagegroup":"38_g20_skyblue_L1/38_g20_skyblue_r1/38_g20_skyblue_L2/38_g20_skyblue_r2","solidwidth":"1280/1280/1280/1280","solidheight":"720/720/720/720","x":"-300","fadetime":"2","id":504},{"type":"largebgtween","duration":"40","xFrom":"-300","xTo":"0","block":"false","id":505},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fltshrd","volume":"0.7","id":506},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":507},{"type":"text","text":"山青青呀水悠悠，月光洒在河上慢慢流♪","id":508},{"type":"text","text":"小船小船摇又晃，我种下种子等花放♪","id":509},{"type":"text","text":"星星挂在天空不说话，外面飘来的种子发芽啦♪","id":510},{"type":"text","text":"你坐上小船去远方，稻花儿飘飘落手旁♪","id":511},{"type":"text","text":"飘呀，飘呀，我送你去远方♪","id":512},{"type":"dialog","id":513},{"type":"gridbg","fadetime":"1","id":514},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":515},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":516},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"......不错的报酬，我很喜欢。","id":517},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"这颗石头是你的了，你的愿望会实现的。","id":518},{"type":"dialog","id":519},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":520},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......哼。","id":521},{"type":"dialog","id":522},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walkfast","volume":"0.6","id":523},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":524},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":525},{"type":"text","text":"小满放下笛子，瞪了旁边的小禾一眼，跺跺脚跑走了。","id":526},{"type":"dialog","id":527},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":528},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"姑娘看起来在生气啊，这是怎么回事？","id":529},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......这首曲子是她给我编的，三年前她送我去考校的时候吹给我的。","id":531},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......我记得的，只是刚刚没反应过来......","id":532},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":533},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"原来如此，有这份心意，倒是难得。","id":534},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"那么，你有没有什么想要和我买的呢？","id":535},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":536},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......我？","id":537},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":538},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"多谢您，但我现在没有什么特别想要的东西。","id":539},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"或者说我想要的，也不可能靠买来得到，还是需要我自己去做才行。","id":540},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":541},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"不妨说来听听？在下也别无所长，只是去过的地方格外多，能卖的东西也格外多些。","id":542},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":544},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"你说什么都能卖，那你难道能卖我一个能喂饱天下人的未来吗？","id":545},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":546},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"......","id":547},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"能。","id":548},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":549},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"你是......什么意思......","id":550},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":551},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"货物越精贵要价当然也越高，你的宏伟理想，你打算用什么价钱来买呢？","id":552},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":553},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"你......","id":554},{"type":"dialog","id":555},{"type":"charslot","id":556},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":557},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":558},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#8$2","duration":"1","id":559},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":560},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#8$2","focus":"m","id":561},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"小禾，剩下那些污染的庄稼我已经收拾了，你看还需要我做——","id":562},{"type":"dialog","id":563},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":564},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#6$2","focus":"m","id":565},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":566},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":567},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你——","id":568},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":569},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着华丽的男性","text":"这位公子为何这么盯着我？难道是与在下认识？","id":570},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":571},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":572},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":573},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"借一步说话！","id":574},{"type":"dialog","id":575},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":576},{"type":"charslot","id":577},{"type":"image","id":578}],"characters":["年","夕","禾生","左乐","小满","土木天师","愤怒的职农","愤怒的土木天师","愤愤不平的职农","禾下午睡的男性","衣着华丽的男性"]}